minjs     — Plotly.js v2.27.0 (MIT, © 2016–2024 Plotly Technologies Inc.).
            Bundled-dependency notices: LICENSES/plotly-2.27.0.LICENSE.txt.
log       — NASA-HTTP web log, July 1995. Lawrence Berkeley Lab Internet Traffic
            Archive; "may be freely redistributed." Collected by Jim Dumoulin
