genome    — E. coli BW4030 resequencing reads, ENA/DDBJ run DRR002013 (study
            DRP000589, submitter: Nankai University). INSDC free & unrestricted.
csv       — NOAA GHCN-Daily (Global Historical Climatology Network–Daily),
            year 2024 observations. U.S. Government work — public domain
            (NOAA/NCEI). A header row was added; truncated at a line boundary.
parquet   — U.S. DOT Bureau of Transportation Statistics, "Reporting Carrier
            On-Time Performance" (TranStats). U.S. Government work — public domain.
            Re-encoded as uncompressed Parquet (all columns string-typed). Core =
            2024-01; large rung = 2022–2024. No personal PII (flight-level records).
            (Replaces the former NYC-TLC taxi file, which was license-encumbered
            open data rather than public domain.)
sqlite    — USDA FoodData Central, SR Legacy (2018-04). U.S. Government work —
            public domain (USDA). Loaded into a multi-table SQLite database with
            join-key indexes; PRAGMA integrity_check = ok.
photo     — "The Blue Marble", NASA, Apollo 17 (AS17-148-22727). Public domain
            (PD-USGov-NASA).
movie     — "Big Buck Bunny" © copyright 2008, Blender Foundation /
            www.bigbuckbunny.org. Licensed under CC-BY 3.0
            (https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/). This corpus includes a
            trimmed/transcoded 120-second excerpt (modified from the original).
weights   — sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2 (Apache-2.0). License text:
            LICENSES/Apache-2.0.txt. (Weights as released; training-data
            provenance not warranted.)
json      — USGS earthquake catalog (M4.5+, 2010–2024), U.S. Geological Survey.
            Public domain (U.S. Government work).

